{"tid":1951401,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港人組織眾籌撐英美醫護","createTime":"2020-03-31T03:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T13:18:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"346fd92df99c3bae8b3d6b3c44153a3a27509496","tid":1951401,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:17:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200330/S6X4R66OXHOAZFTWRIALSXHMUY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200330%2FS6X4R66OXHOAZFTWRIALSXHMUY%2F&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtEwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=81d599b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200330%2FS6X4R66OXHOAZFTWRIALSXHMUY%2F&h=fdd88091\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200330/S6X4R66OXHOAZFTWRIALSXHMUY/</a><br />\n<br />\n港人組織眾籌撐英美醫護<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200330/large/1585498395_b3cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200330%2Flarge%2F1585498395_b3cf.jpg&h=e4b2fcf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHongkongers4US向美國醫護送出物資。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】英、美兩國正受武漢肺炎疫情打擊，兩地港人組織均發起眾籌，支援當地醫護購買保護物資，作為回報兩地人民聲援港人反送中運動，在英國發起眾籌的前英國領事館職員鄭文傑直言，希望英國人明白，港人在危難時刻仍與英國人民同在，為未來政治游說打好基礎。<br />\n<br />\n早前16個在美國支持香港爭取民主運動的團體組成#Hongkongers4US發起眾籌，集合美國各地港人團體力量，希望支援美國醫護人員對抗武漢肺炎，亦感激美國一直為保衞香港民主自由而發聲，特別感謝美國議會去年通過《香港人權與民主法案》，他們已向美國不少醫護送出口罩等防疫物資，他們眾籌目標為30萬美元，目前已籌到逾16萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鄭文傑：為政治游說打好基礎<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：武漢肺炎疫情最新發展<br />\n<br />\n英國方面，則有鄭文傑牽頭的The Umbrella Union為醫護眾籌，鄭接受本報訪問時透露，英國目前情況跟香港不同，最大難題是未能處理物流運輸，「所以最直接係透過眾籌再支援係最好」，而眾籌反應非常理想，短短四日已籌到逾20萬港元，是目標金額雙倍，部份款項將交予英國國民保健服務（NHS）下重災疫情區醫院，註明供前線醫護之用；部份款項捐至國家緊急情況基金會（National Emergencies Trust），部份亦會捐予英國全國醫生及護士公會。<br />\n<br />\n鄭文傑不諱言如此「民間交往」背後有政治目的，「希望向國際發出訊息，唔係香港人需要時先叫大家Stand with Hong Kong，而係其他地方有需要，我哋都願意Stand with佢哋；疫情本身都唔只係疫情，亦同政治有關。」鄭坦言，希望利用今次行動為將來在英國作有關香港政治游說「做定基礎工作」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳玨明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200330/large/1585498392_3626.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200330%2Flarge%2F1585498392_3626.jpg&h=f6d795f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭文傑"},{"pid":"c0625a1998db1e531427afda4feee73a2a2aafe7","tid":1951401,"uid":169074,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:24:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"337d2e3647ccf6b1e76bf0e82384100e34e2719d","tid":1951401,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:26:37.000Z","msg":"開始日日都有還押幾個月手足上庭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1951351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1951351</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d6c697a2f6816a88f0cac3f3852508bb2ba82da1","tid":1951401,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:27:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f876f528fab48ce069ca76d749b43840bbde7a0","tid":1951401,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:27:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f1c8ca740ead0184c816ec177f0b11f163cd9de","tid":1951401,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:29:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8455257da7e5cf4333691f3e5d08d67028a1431","tid":1951401,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:33:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0aabaf813ef0e21f22cc185c36af55b9e22af867","tid":1951401,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:33:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"815d72fafb30b0746087b34cd7b15593bc806397","tid":1951401,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:38:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8967baa3c2954f1930c757bba6ece6294c7804b","tid":1951401,"uid":169074,"like":0